{"product_id":"nurme-neroli-collagen-renewal-night-cream-50ml","title":"NURME Neroli Collagen Renewal Night Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis night cream deeply moisturizes and nourishes, restoring collagen and elasticity lost due to early signs of aging. High in vitamins C and E, along with passion fruit oil, it hydrates and revitalizes the skin, making it youthful and elastic.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNeroli oil, derived from bitter orange blossoms, offers powerful antimicrobial and antibacterial properties, making it ideal for acne-prone skin and clogged pores. It regulates sebum production, balancing oily skin. Rich in antioxidants and vitamin E, neroli oil provides anti-aging and anti-acne benefits, reducing inflammation and redness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis product is packaged in a recyclable polypropylene airless bottle. The airless packaging prevents air exposure, ensuring microbiological purity and extending the shelf life of natural cosmetics.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply to clean skin after other serums or creams. Allow to absorb completely.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Citrus Aurantium Dulcis Flower Water*, Aqua*, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride**, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil*, Glycerin**, Passiflora Edulis Seed Oil*, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter*, Betain**, Polyglyceryl-3 Methylglucose Distearate**, Glyceryl Stearate**, Cetearyl Alcohol**, Myristyl Myristate**, Sodium Levulinate**, Ascorbyl Palmitate**, Sodium Anisate**, Panthenol*, Benzyl Alcohol**, Tocopherol**, Lactic Acid**, Sodium Hyaluronate**, Allantoin*, Sodium Benzoate**, Potassium Sorbate**, Xanthan Gum**, Hectorite**, Cellulose**, Passiflora Incarnata Extract*, Citrus Aurantium Flower Oil*, Limonene***, Linalool***. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* Natural origin\u003cbr\u003e** Natural cosmetics approved ingredient\u003cbr\u003e***Occurs naturally in essential oils\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915905012039,"sku":null,"price":27.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-neroli-collagen-renewal-night-cream-50ml-207317.jpg?v=1739897174","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/nurme-neroli-collagen-renewal-night-cream-50ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}